# Server Configuration Template

⚠️ **DO NOT COMMIT THIS FILE WITH REAL DATA**

Copy this file to `docs/doc.server.md` and fill with your actual credentials.
The file `docs/doc.server.md` is ignored by git.

## Production Server

```
host: your-server-ip-or-domain
port: your-app-port (e.g., 3105)
user: your-ssh-username
```

## SSH Access

```
# Test connection
ssh your-username@your-server-ip

# Deploy path
/home/your-username/htdocs/your-domain
```

## Notes

- Keep this information secure
- Never commit real credentials to git
- Use environment variables when possible
- Rotate credentials regularly
